data.heading: Flexible Cables
data.description: Flexible Cables. 300/500 V CU/PVC/PVC 2, 3, 4, 5 cores up to 25 mm². Flexible stranded copper conductor Class 5, polyvinyl chloride insulation, Typical uses for such cables include cable tray routing, portable power equipment, wind and solar energy, oil and gas applications, and more. Standard Lenth is 100 yards
